o"><h5 class="title"><a href="https://www.foxnews.com/world/italy-nabs-wanted-algerian-foreign-fighter-back-from-syria">Italy nabs wanted Algerian foreign fighter back from Syria</a></h5><div class="meta"><!----><!----></div></div></article></li></ul></div><!----></section><div class="ad-container desktop"><div data-ad-pos="desktop" data-ad-size="300x251" data-ad-lz="" class="ad gpt "></div><span class="advert-txt">ADVERTISEMENT</span></div><div data-uid="ar-11" class="vendor-unit"></div></div></div></aside></div></article></main></div><div class="post-content"></div></div><footer class="site-footer"><div class="footer-upper"><div class="section-nav"><div class="inner"><nav><h6 class="nav-title"><a href="/us">U.S.</a></h6><ul><li class="nav-item"><a href="/category/us/crime">Crime</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="/category/us/military">Military</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="/category/us/education">Education</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="/category/us/terror">Terror</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="/category/us/immigration">Immigration</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="/category/us/economy">Economy</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="/category/us/personal-freedoms">Personal Freedoms</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="/category/news-events/fox-news-investigates">Fox News Investigates</a></li></ul></nav><nav><h6 class="nav-title"><a href="/world">World</a></h6><ul><li class="nav-item"><a href="/category/world/united-nations">U.N.</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="/category/world/conflicts">Conflicts</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="/category/world/terrorism">Terrorism</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="/category/world/disasters">Disasters</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="/category/world/global-economy">Global Economy</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="/category/world/environment">Environment</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="/category/world/world-religion">Religion</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a href="/category